overview: Slednecks 16 showcases elite snowmobilers pushing the limits of not only their machine but the sport of Snowmobiling. This season (2012-2013) the slednecks crew comes through again with another sick Slednecks DVD to keep their fans up-to-date on the progression of the Slednecks team. From the deepest of powder days, to technical riding, to huge drops and hits, Slednecks Sixteen DVD or Blu-Ray includes all the craziness from the award winning crew. Captured beautifully on HD and viewable by all ages!
title: Slednecks 16
